!   ai-article.ecs
!   Standalone article: Building Applications with EasyCoder and Claude Code

    script Article

    div Container
    module ShowdownModule
    variable Script

    create Container in body
    set the style of Container to `max-width:800px;margin:2em auto;padding:0 2em`

    require js `dist/plugins/showdown.js`

    rest get Script from `/resources/ecs/showdown.ecs?v=` cat now
    run Script with Container as ShowdownModule

    rest get Script from `/resources/md/ai-article.md?v=` cat now
    send Script to ShowdownModule
    stop
